are engineering federighi oversees the development of ios macos and apples common operating system engineering teams his teams are responsible for delivering the software at the heart of apples products including the user interface applications and frameworks contents  early life  career  next  return to apple  public image  see also  references early lifeedit after graduating from acalanes high school in lafayette california federighi earned a master of science degree in computer science and a bachelor of science in electrical engineering and computer science from the university of california berkeley he is of italian descent federighi was married as of  and has four children all daughters careeredit nextedit federighi worked under steve jobs at next where he led development of the enterprise objects framework he joined apple when it acquired next in  but then left it in  for the enterprise it company ariba where he was chief technology officer return to appleedit he returned to apple in  and led macos engineering on march   federighi succeeded bertrand serlet as vice president of mac software engineering at apple and on august   he was promoted to senior vice president reporting to ceo tim cook on october   upon the announcement of scott forstalls departure from apple his role was expanded to encompass ios in addition to mac software engineering as of september  federighi is reported to own more than  shares of apple stock worth about us million public imageedit within the community of apple users and developers federighi is known for his energetic presentations of new apple software frequently featuring absurdist humor such as references to his somewhat bouffant hair use of new software features to organize events such as office karaoke parties and camping trips and his claimed love of the band rush his first appearance onstage during a major apple event was at wwdc  where he helped bertrand serlet introduce mac os x snow leopard he made another appearance during s back to the mac presentation showing off mac os x lion he introduced ios  and os x mavericks at apples wwdc  developer conference and ios  and os x yosemite at wwdc  at wwdc  he delivered most of apples hour main openingday presentation introducing ios  and os x  el capitan and revealing plans to release apple’s new programming language swift as an opensource project in september  he demoed d touch in the new iphone s at wwdc  federighi introduced ios  and macos  sierra and said that the yearold os x would be rebranded as macos in tune with the naming scheme used for ios tvos and watchos he emphasized the use of widgets on the ios lock screen and announced new apis for siri and imessage that would be open to all developers see alsoedit angela ahrendts jony ive dan riccio referencesedit  apple press info  craig federighi apple retrieved  january    a b craig federighi apple’s vice president of mac software engineering  dan riccio apple’s vice president of hardware engineering join apple’s executive team as senior vice presidents apple press release  aug  retrieved  aug    httpinvestingbusinessweekcomresearchstockspeoplepersonasppersonidtickeraaplpreviouscapidprevioustitleappleinc  httpoverpressitcraigfederighilitaloamericanostarivoluzionandoapple  whitney lance tim cook talks apple secrecy on macs th anniversary cnet retrieved  november    spooky fun ahead los altos offers an array of halloween activities los altos town crier retrieved  november    josh lowensohn  march  who is apples new mac guy cnet retrieved  july    bertrand serlet to leave apple apple press release apple march   retrieved  june    apple announces changes to increase collaboration across hardware software  services apple inc  archived from the original on october   retrieved    craig federighi insider trading overview wwwinsidermolecom retrieved    superman gave  of the apple keynote mashable retrieved  june    craig federighi may give apple a new jolt usa today retrieved  june    one of apple