ence in electrical engineering and computer science from the university of california berkeley riccio as senior vice president of hardware engineering will lead the mac® iphone® ipad® and ipod® engineering teams he has been instrumental in all of apple’s ipad products since the first generation ipad riccio joined apple in  as vice president of product design and has been a key contributor to most of apple’s hardware over his career dan earned a bachelor’s degree in mechanical engineering from the university of massachusetts amherst in  apple designs macs the best personal computers in the world along with os x ilife iwork and professional software apple leads the digital music revolution with its ipods and itunes online store apple has reinvented the mobile phone with its revolutionary iphone and app store and is defining the future of mobile media and computing devices with ipad press contactkristin huguetapplekhuguetapplecom  apple the apple logo mac mac os macintosh iphone ipad and ipod are trademarks of apple other company and product names may be trademarks of their respective owners the latest news for journalistsread more craig federighi on macrumors got a tip for us let us know a send us an email b anonymous form close x             front page mac blog ios blog roundups airport apple car apple deals apple pay apple stores apple tv apple vr project apple watch series  carplay displays homepod imac imac pro ios  ios  ipad  ipad mini   ipad pro iphone s iphone  iphone  iphone se ipod nano ipod shuffle ipod touch mac mini mac pro macbook macbook air macbook pro macos high sierra macos sierra tvos  watchos  watchos  buyers guide forums homepod ios  iphone  iphone  macos high sierra imac pro macbook pro watchos  watchos  apple watch series  ipad pro iphone s macbook tvos  apple tv iphone se apple car apple deals carplay ipad mini   mac mini mac pro macbook air macos sierra ios  apple vr project imac ipad  displays apple stores airport apple pay ipod nano ipod shuf