ent of scott forstalls departure from apple his role was expanded to encompass ios in addition to mac software engineering as of september  federighi is reported to own more than  shares of apple stock worth about us million public imageedit within the community of apple users and developers federighi is known for his energetic presentations of new apple software frequently featuring absurdist humor such as references to his somewhat bouffant hair use of new software features to organize events such as office karaoke parties and camping trips and his claimed love of the band rush his first appearance onstage during a major apple event was at wwdc  where he helped bertrand serlet introduce mac os x snow leopard he made another appearance during s back to the mac presentation showing off mac os x lion he introduced ios  and os x mavericks at apples wwdc  developer conference and ios  and os x yosemite at wwdc  at wwdc  he delivered most of apples hour main openingday presentation introducing ios  and os x  el capitan and revealing plans to release apple’s new programming language swift as an opensource project in september  he demoed d touch in the new iphone s at wwdc  federighi introduced ios  and macos  sierra and said that the yearold os x would be rebranded as macos in tune with the naming scheme used for ios tvos and watchos he emphasized the use of widgets on the ios lock screen and announced new apis for siri and imessage that would be open to all developers see alsoedit angela ahrendts jony ive dan riccio referencesedit  apple press info  craig federighi apple retrieved  january    a b craig federighi apple’s vice president of mac software engineering  dan riccio apple’s vice president of hardware engineering join apple’s executive team as senior vice presidents apple press release  aug  retrieved  aug    httpinvestingbusinessweekcomresearchstockspeoplepersonasppersonidtickeraaplpreviouscapidprevioustitleappleinc  httpoverpressitcraigfederighilitaloamericanos