i and imessage that would be open to all developers see alsoedit angela ahrendts jony ive dan riccio referencesedit  apple press info  craig federighi apple retrieved  january    a b craig federighi apple’s vice president of mac software engineering  dan riccio apple’s vice president of hardware engineering join apple’s executive team as senior vice presidents apple press release  aug  retrieved  aug    httpinvestingbusinessweekcomresearchstockspeoplepersonasppersonidtickeraaplpreviouscapidprevioustitleappleinc  httpoverpressitcraigfederighilitaloamericanostarivoluzionandoapple  whitney lance tim cook talks apple secrecy on macs th anniversary cnet retrieved  november    spooky fun ahead los altos offers an array of halloween activities los altos town crier retrieved  november    josh lowensohn  march  who is apples new mac guy cnet retrieved  july    bertrand serlet to leave apple apple press release apple march   retrieved  june    apple announces changes to increase collaboration across hardware software  services apple inc  archived from the original on october   retrieved    craig federighi insider trading overview wwwinsidermolecom retrieved    superman gave  of the apple keynote mashable retrieved  june    craig federighi may give apple a new jolt usa today retrieved  june    one of apples biggest success stories takes a huge leap forward business insider retrieved jun    v t e apple inc history outline founders steve jobs steve wozniak ronald wayne board of directors current james a bell tim cook ceo albert gore jr robert a iger andrea jung arthur d levinson chairman ronald d sugar susan l wagner former fred d anderson gil amelio bill campbell mickey drexler larry ellison steve jobs delano lewis mike markkula arthur rock eric schmidt john sculley edgar s woolard jr jerry york executives current tim cook ceo jonathan ive cdo jeff williams coo luca maestri cfo angela ahrendts philip w schiller eddy cue craig federighi dan riccio johny srouji bruce sewell lisa 